.cloudos-alert .alert-text-container h1 { font-family: "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; font-size: 19px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 23px; color: var(--theme-color-labelPrimary); text-align: center; padding-block: 12px 15px; }

.cloudos-alert[dir="ltr"] .alert-text-container h1, .cloudos-alert[dir="rtl"] .alert-text-container h1, [dir="ltr"] .cloudos-alert .alert-text-container h1, [dir="rtl"] .cloudos-alert .alert-text-container h1 { padding-top: 12px; padding-bottom: 15px; }

.cloudos-alert .alert-text-container p { font-family: "SF Pro Text", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 20px; color: var(--theme-color-labelSecondary); text-align: center; margin-block-end: 10px; }

.cloudos-toolbar { position: sticky; inset-block-start: 0px; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; user-select: none; block-size: 44px; min-block-size: 44px; box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0px; padding-inline: 16px 6px; }
.cloudos-toolbar .app-title { font-family: "SF Pro Display", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; font-size: 21px; font-weight: 600; margin-inline-start: 1px; }
.cloudos-toolbar.login { background-image: none; background-color: rgba(251, 251, 253, 0.5); border-block-end: 1px solid rgba(251, 251, 253, 0.5); }
.cloudos-toolbar.login::before { content: ""; position: absolute; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); inset: 0px; z-index: -1; }
.cloudos-toolbar .icloud-logo { display: flex; -webkit-box-flex: 0; flex: 0 0 auto; margin-inline-start: -2px; margin-block-start: 1px; }
.cloudos-toolbar .icloud-logo a { display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; }
